<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/george-soros" title="George Soros" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="3b337c0246f86f2c0f1b240b" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="george-soros" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/george-soros"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">George Soros</span></a></span>
            argues that the EU cannot be saved without transforming its political party systems.
        </p>
    </header>
