        <h2 class="listing__title">
            <a href="/commentary/economic-outlook-for-2019-main-factors-by-nouriel-roubini-2019-02">A Mixed Economic Bag in 2019</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="listing__excerpt">
                <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-08T11:00Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 8, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/nouriel-roubini" title="Nouriel Roubini" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="60bc7c0246f86f2c0f9a2f0b" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="nouriel-roubini" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/nouriel-roubini"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Nouriel Roubini</span></a></span>
            explains why the global outlook for the coming year will depend on a broad range of interrelated factors.
        </p>
    </header>
    <footer class="listing__footer">
