    </article>

    

    <ul class="list list--indented u-hidden" data-id="cr-">
    </ul>
    <div class="comment__reply-refresh u-hidden">
        A new reply to this comment has been posted.&nbsp;<button>Load?</button>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="comment " data-line-id="">
    <article class="comment__item" data-comment-id="59a7096c1d12552908c72253" data-comment-author="bob-trumpkin" itemprop="comment" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Comment">
        <header>
            <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
                <a href="/profile/bob-trumpkin" class="nmd-item__name"><span itemprop="name">Bob Trumpkin</span></a>
            </span>
            &nbsp;<time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2016-09-28T23:15Z">Sep 28, 2016</time>
        </header>
        <div itemprop="text">
            <p>
                &quot;Moreover, 50 of America&#x2019;s most senior Republican national security officials have signed a letter warning that Trump &#x201C;would put at risk our country&#x2019;s national security and well-being.&#x201D; &quot;&#xD;<br/>Establishment warmongering Republicans are against Trump, what a surprise.  Who cares if Clinton put classified emails on her private server, she&#x27;ll keep the status quo going for four more years.  Yeah bipartisonship !
            </p>
        </div>

            <button class="comment__reply u-hidden" aria-controls="comment__new__controls" aria-expanded="false">Reply</button>

    </article>

    

    <ul class="list list--indented u-hidden" data-id="cr-">
