            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/commentary/sovereign-bonds-lower-pension-fund-risk-by-carmen-reinhart-and-christoph-trebesch-2019-02">Risky Retirement Business</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T16:33Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/carmen-reinhart" title="Carmen M. Reinhart" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="543bbfeb4a4231113cafaea3" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="carmen-reinhart" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/carmen-reinhart"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Carmen M. Reinhart</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/christoph-trebesch" title="Christoph Trebesch" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5925d78f2bd5d21908e9c2b9" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="christoph-trebesch" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/christoph-trebesch"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Christoph Trebesch</span></a></span>
                examine an asset class that could provide what yield-hungry pension-fund managers are looking for.

                
            </div>

