                <a href="/commentary/plan-to-avoid-war-in-venezuela-by-jeffrey-d-sachs-and-francisco-rodriguez-2-2019-02">How to Avoid a War in Venezuela</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T15:01Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/jeffrey-d-sachs" title="Jeffrey D. Sachs" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="537b7a0c2888131684dc8170" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="jeffrey-d-sachs" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/jeffrey-d-sachs"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Jeffrey D. Sachs</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/francisco-rodr-guez-2" title="Francisco Rodr&#xED;guez" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5c7544f878b6c73a48cef5a7" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="francisco-rodr-guez-2" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/francisco-rodr-guez-2"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Francisco Rodr&#xED;guez</span></a></span>
