        <header class="listing__header">
            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/commentary/isis-returnees-begum-muthana-by-bj-rn-ihler-and-fatima-zaman-2019-02">Why Western Countries Must Accept Returning Extremists</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T12:59Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/bj-rn-ihler" title="Bj&#xF8;rn Ihler" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5c7533de78b6c73a48bd6dcc" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="bj-rn-ihler" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/bj-rn-ihler"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Bj&#xF8;rn Ihler</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/fatima-zaman" title="Fatima Zaman" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5c7533de78b6c73a48bd6e41" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="fatima-zaman" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/fatima-zaman"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Fatima Zaman</span></a></span>
                say that denying former ISIS fighters and brides their right to due process is bound to backfire.

                
            </div>

        </header>
