        <header class="listing__header">
            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/podcasts/the-trade-war-to-end-all-trade-wars">The Trade War to End All Trade Wars?</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T12:36Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/elmira-bayrasli" title="Elmira Bayrasli" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="55144ab6bc1f5a1054ecff3c" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="elmira-bayrasli" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/elmira-bayrasli"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Elmira Bayrasli</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/ann-lee-1" title="Ann Lee" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5c732dfc78b6c73c688ad213" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="ann-lee-1" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/ann-lee-1"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Ann Lee</span></a></span>
                discuss the ongoing trade negotiations between the US and China.

                
            </div>

        </header>
        <footer class="listing__footer">
