        <header class="listing__header">
            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/commentary/global-compact-opposition-migration-development-by-mahmoud-mohieldin-and-dilip-ratha-2019-02">Migration Myths vs. Economic Facts</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T11:53Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/mahmoud-mohieldin" title="Mahmoud Mohieldin" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="22cf1f0446f86f500e57f101" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="mahmoud-mohieldin" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/mahmoud-mohieldin"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Mahmoud Mohieldin</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/dilip-ratha" title="Dilip Ratha" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="53d25acb4a4231129c43e4d3" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="dilip-ratha" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/dilip-ratha"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Dilip Ratha</span></a></span>
                set the record straight on why people move to other countries &#x2013; and what they do when they get there.

                
            </div>

        </header>
