        <header class="listing__header">
            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/commentary/africa-development-investment-financing-needs-by-guillaume-arditti-2019-02">Closing Africa&#x2019;s Financing Gap</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-26T10:01Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 26, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/guillaume-arditti" title="Guillaume Arditti" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5beec31978b6c76074c67377" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="guillaume-arditti" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/guillaume-arditti"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Guillaume Arditti</span></a></span>
                says private-sector debt funds can play a major role in meeting the continent&#x27;s huge investment needs.

                
            </div>

        </header>
        <footer class="listing__footer">
