        <header class="listing__header">
            <h2 class="listing__title">
                <a href="/commentary/neoliberalism-versus-green-new-deal-by-anders-fremstad-and-mark-paul-2019-02">Overcoming the Ideology of Climate Inaction</a>
            </h2>
            <div class="listing__excerpt">

                        <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2019-02-25T16:49Z" class="vl-divider">Feb 25, 2019</time>

<span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><a href="/columnist/anders-fremstad" title="Anders Fremstad" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5c74173e78b6c73c687d8e3e" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="anders-fremstad" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/anders-fremstad"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Anders Fremstad</span></a></span><span class="byline " itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"> & <a href="/columnist/mark-paul" title="Mark Paul" itemprop="url" data-entity-type="member" data-entity-id="5b32673c78b6c7088c9f2cc8" data-language="english" data-event-action="click" data-entity-link-name="mark-paul" class="track-event" data-href-original="/columnist/mark-paul"><span class="listing__author author" itemprop="name">Mark Paul</span></a></span>
                argue that neoliberal policymaking continues to fuel global warming and stand in the way of solutions.

                
            </div>

        </header>
        <footer class="listing__footer">
